author: taylor
msg: Refine request parameter processing to better support embedding in and extending other portals
Allow PortletURLProvider to take a role in contributing to request parameter processing
The PortletRequestImpl was directly tied to Pluto's implementation of non-encoded URLs and request parameters
The PortletURLProvider now contributes to the parameters without being so tightly coupled to Pluto's implementation
Refactored and moved up implementation of *RequestImpl, factoring out common implementations where duplications found
